        "heading_kQYPDp": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>Sinks & Tapware</p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_DXGPFE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sinks and tapware form the functional centre of the kitchen, and selecting the right combination plays a key role in both usability and overall design cohesion. The New Year Sale includes a focused range of sinks and tapware from leading brands known for precision engineering, material quality, and long-term performance.<br/><br/>Explore <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke\"><strong>Franke sinks and tapware</strong></a>, offering integrated solutions designed to work seamlessly together. Franke is widely specified for kitchens where durability, refined design, and practical performance are essential, making it a strong option for both new builds and renovations.<br/><br/>For tapware-only upgrades, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella_vista\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella_vista\"><strong>Bella Vista tapware</strong></a> provides contemporary mixer designs with clean profiles and balanced proportions. These ranges suit modern kitchen environments where visual consistency and ease of use are prioritised.<br/><br/>Sink-focused solutions are available from<strong> </strong><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima\"><strong>Seima</strong></a>, selected for their functional bowl configurations, robust materials, and suitability across a range of kitchen layouts. Seima offers options that support both minimalist aesthetics and practical daily use.<br/><br/>Together, these brands provide targeted sink and tapware solutions that prioritise performance, design cohesion, and long-term value within the kitchen.</p>"
          }
