          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>Mirrors & Vanities</p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_GEfrVc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mirrors and vanities play a defining role in how a bathroom looks, functions, and feels on a daily basis. Beyond storage, these elements influence spatial balance, lighting, and how efficiently the room supports everyday routines. The New Year Sale includes a focused selection of mirrors and vanities from established brands known for quality finishes, considered proportions, and practical design suited to Australian bathrooms.<br/><br/>Explore <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/otti\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/otti\">Otti mirrors, shaving cabinets,  and vanities</a>, designed to support clean, contemporary bathroom layouts with an emphasis on usability and visual restraint. Otti ranges are valued for their integrated storage solutions, streamlined profiles, and finishes that work well across modern and transitional interiors, making them a strong option for both renovations and new builds.<br/><br/>For additional design flexibility, discover <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\">Fienza mirrors and vanities</a>, offering a broad range of styles that balance form and function. Fienza products are selected for their material quality, thoughtful detailing, and ability to integrate seamlessly into a variety of bathroom layouts, from compact spaces to larger, statement bathrooms.<br/><br/>Mirror design continues to favour clarity and simplicity, supporting improved lighting and a more open feel within the room, while vanity configurations focus on efficient storage without visual bulk. When selected together, mirrors and vanities help create bathrooms that feel organised, balanced, and cohesive, supporting everyday use while maintaining a refined overall aesthetic.<br/><br/>Together, Otti and Fienza provide practical, well-designed mirror and vanity solutions that prioritise durability, usability, and long-term design consistency.</p>"
          }
        },
