    "rich_text_kfMPD4": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_8HQe3z": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>Baths & Showers</p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_MEwLPf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Showers and baths are foundational to both comfort and functionality in the bathroom, with modern design prioritising efficient layouts, durable materials, and long-term usability. Current preferences favour bathrooms that feel open and uncluttered, where baths and showers are selected based on space, daily routines, and ease of maintenance rather than purely decorative appeal.<br/><br/>Bath selection continues to centre on form, comfort, and practicality. Freestanding baths are commonly chosen for larger bathrooms where they can act as a visual anchor, while inset and back-to-wall bath designs suit more compact layouts that require efficient use of space. The New Year Sale includes bath options from established manufacturers such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/decina\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/decina\">Decina</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima\">Seima</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\">Fienza</a>, supporting a range of bathroom configurations and design approaches without compromising on build quality or comfort.<br/><br/>Shower design continues to move toward walk-in formats, frameless screens, and simplified layouts that improve accessibility and reduce visual noise. The focus is on reliable water delivery, efficient drainage, and surfaces that are easy to clean and maintain over time. Shower systems and fittings from brands including <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix\">Phoenix</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/caroma\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/caroma\">Caroma</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella_vista\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella_vista\">Bella Vista</a> support bathrooms where performance and consistency are prioritised across fixtures.<br/><br/>Shower floor solutions also play an important role in overall usability, contributing to water management, safety, and long-term durability within the shower zone. Options from suppliers such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/decina\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/decina\">Domus Living</a> help create bathrooms that function efficiently while maintaining a clean, resolved finish.<br/><br/>Together, these shower and bath solutions support bathrooms that are practical, balanced, and designed for everyday use, making it easier to plan spaces that remain functional and visually cohesive over time.</p>"
          }
        },
