    "rich_text_ahk48e": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_p8KRAp": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>Basins & Tapware</p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_XkcehH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Basins and tapware work together to define both the visual balance and everyday usability of the bathroom. Contemporary bathroom design continues to favour clean forms, efficient layouts, and pairings that feel intentional rather than decorative. The focus is on proportion, ease of use, and finishes that integrate naturally with surrounding materials and cabinetry.<br/><br/>Basin selection is increasingly driven by how the space is used and how the basin sits within the overall layout. Above-counter and semi-recessed basins are commonly chosen to introduce subtle visual interest, while integrated and inset designs support a more streamlined appearance. The New Year Sale includes basin options from established suppliers such as <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima-basins\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/seima-basins\">Seima basins</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza-basins\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza-basins\">Fienza basins</a>, offering a range of forms and finishes suited to modern bathroom environments without unnecessary visual complexity.<br/><br/>Tapware selection plays a supporting role, ensuring comfortable operation and visual alignment with the basin itself. Bathroom tapware trends continue to favour refined profiles, smooth operation, and finishes that complement neutral palettes and textured surfaces. Tapware ranges from <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella-vista-bathroom\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella-vista-bathroom\">Bella Vista basin tapware</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix-bathroom-tapware\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix-bathroom-tapware\">Phoenix bathroom tapware</a> support bathrooms where consistency across fixtures and long-term reliability are key considerations.<br/><br/>When selected together, basins and tapware contribute to bathrooms that feel balanced, practical, and visually resolved, supporting everyday use while maintaining clarity in the overall design.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
