    "featured_collection_Ub4MbX": {
      "type": "featured-collection",
      "settings": {
        "title": "Appliances",
        "heading_size": "h1",
        "description": "<p>Appliances play a central role in how a kitchen functions on a daily basis, influencing cooking performance, efficiency, and overall layout. Contemporary kitchen design prioritises appliances that integrate cleanly into cabinetry, support consistent results, and suit a wide range of cooking habits, from everyday family use to more considered entertaining. <br/><br/>The New Year Sale includes a broad selection of kitchen appliances spanning key categories such as fridges, ovens, cooktops, rangehoods, dishwashers, microwaves, and alfresco cooking solutions. Selection is increasingly driven by practical factors including cooking capacity, heat control, ventilation efficiency, and how appliances work together within the space, rather than individual statement pieces.</p><p>Cooking appliances remain a core focus, with ovens and cooktops selected based on reliability, temperature accuracy, and layout flexibility. Ventilation is equally important, with rangehoods specified to manage steam, heat, and odours effectively while maintaining visual balance within the kitchen. Refrigeration continues to be an essential consideration, with fridge designs chosen to suit storage needs, kitchen size, and integration preferences.<br/><br/>Dishwashers and microwaves support everyday efficiency, with an emphasis on quiet operation, intuitive controls, and durability in high-use environments. Alfresco appliances are also increasingly specified, extending cooking and entertaining spaces outdoors while maintaining consistent performance and material quality.<br/><br/>Appliance ranges from established manufacturers including <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/electrolux\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/electrolux\">Electrolux</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/euro-appliances\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/euro-appliances\">Euro Appliances</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg\">Smeg</a> provide options across all major categories, supporting kitchens that prioritise functionality, design cohesion, and long-term usability.</p><p>Together, these appliance solutions allow kitchens to be planned holistically, ensuring each component works efficiently within the overall layout while supporting consistent performance over time.</p>",
        "show_description": false,
        "description_style": "body",
        "collection": "new-year-appliances-sale",
        "products_to_show": 4,
        "columns_desktop": 4,
        "full_width": false,
