    "rich_text_NDfcxF": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_krGALd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>National Delivery Across Australia</p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_NVP8Md": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Cook & Bathe offers national delivery across Australia, making it easier to access premium kitchen, bathroom, and laundry products no matter where you are located. Our delivery network is structured to support metropolitan, regional, and selected remote locations, allowing customers outside major cities to source high-quality products without relying on local availability.</p><p>National delivery supports homeowners, renovators, builders, and designers who require consistent access to trusted brands and curated ranges, regardless of state or postcode. This approach ensures product selection is not limited by geography, providing the same access to sinks, tapware, appliances, baths, showers, and bathroom fixtures across the country.</p><p>Delivery methods are tailored to suit the size and nature of each product, with careful handling for larger and heavier items to support safe transit and condition on arrival. </p><p>By offering Australia-wide delivery, Cook & Bathe supports national renovation projects, remote builds, and customers seeking specialist products that may not be available locally, ensuring consistent access to considered design and dependable performance wherever your project is based.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_krGALd",
        "text_NVP8Md"
